1265
01:16:47.002 --> 01:16:50.242
What we found by taking this dual targeting,

1266
01:16:50.722 --> 01:16:54.502
avidity-based approach was that we could dial in and

1267
01:16:54.702 --> 01:16:58.582
out the amount of activity. And I don't have time to go

