1346
01:21:51.490 --> 01:21:54.770
Again, we see very good activity in preclinical models.

1347
01:21:55.090 --> 01:21:58.630
This is a gastric cancer xenograft that expresses both

1348
01:21:58.710 --> 01:22:02.630
