01:44:24.916 --> 01:44:26.376
for every individual

1719
01:44:28.836 --> 01:44:29.676
T cell in the

1720
01:44:31.956 --> 01:44:32.376
product,

1721
01:44:34.036 --> 01:44:37.536
the reactivity at the cell level. So this characterization

1722
01:44:37.576 --> 01:44:41.306
