1758
01:46:47.825 --> 01:46:51.436
And especially the IL-2 pathway activity was interesting.

1759
01:46:51.796 --> 01:46:55.096
As I mentioned to you in the beginning, we grow these cells in high doses of

1760
01:46:55.136 --> 01:46:57.196
