1774
01:47:45.056 --> 01:47:47.916
non-responding high patients. So

1775
01:47:48.576 --> 01:47:52.336
collectively, these data identify CD25 positive

1776
01:47:52.396 --> 01:47:56.296
tumor-reactive Goldilock states that couples tumor recognition with

1777
01:47:56.376 --> 01:48:00.136
