1788
01:48:34.376 --> 01:48:37.416
and in orange here are the reactive ones.

1789
01:48:37.446 --> 01:48:40.876
And results demonstrate, and when you look here at these tumor-reactive

1790
01:48:42.876 --> 01:48:46.456
cells, that there's a higher fraction of predicted

1791
01:48:46.536 --> 01:48:47.826
tumor-reactive clones

1792
01:48:48.976 --> 01:48:52.516
in the blood of responders compared to these non-responder

1793
01:48:52.556 --> 01:48:54.716
cohorts. But tumor-reactive

1794
01:48:56.536 --> 01:49:00.176
cells here seem to decrease over time

1795
01:49:00.536 --> 01:49:04.296
at week 12, and we assume that this has something to do with the

1796
01:49:04.316 --> 01:49:07.176
