1797
01:49:08.996 --> 01:49:12.896
So using single-cell RNA sequencing, T cell receptor sequencing, and

1798
01:49:12.916 --> 01:49:16.856
CyTOF sequencing analysis of tumor digest used to manufacture

1799
01:49:16.956 --> 01:49:20.896
