1806
01:49:42.336 --> 01:49:45.996
transcriptional profile, which expanded into the drug product.

1807
01:49:46.596 --> 01:49:50.176
In responder patients, T cells appear to expand in circulation

1808
01:49:50.636 --> 01:49:54.396
following TIL infusion. In non-responders, expanding cells are mostly

1809
01:49:54.496 --> 01:49:56.156
