1829
01:51:07.856 --> 01:51:11.626
So it may be more complicated to grow TIL from other indications.

1830
01:51:13.536 --> 01:51:17.416
Lastly, T cell features within tumor digests are predictive of clinical

1831
01:51:17.476 --> 01:51:20.966
